rows.label: qst201105_0010
rows.name: As expected, there's no one here either.

rows.label: qst201105_0020
rows.name:
If last time was anything to go by, somebody's probably
having a cheeky peek at us right about now.

rows.label: qst201105_0030
rows.name:
Hey! I know you can hear me! Stop creeping
around like a coward and show yourself!

rows.label: qst201105_0040
rows.name: Another one of those...?

rows.label: qst201105_0050
rows.name:
What are you trying to tell us
with all these lances?!

rows.label: qst201105_0060
rows.name:
Stop beating around the bush!
Come out, and tell us what you want to our faces!

rows.label: qst201105_0070
rows.name: Or are you afraid of me?!

rows.label: qst201105_0075
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]ADLIB

rows.label: qst201105_0080
rows.name: [ML:undisp ](gasp)

rows.label: qst201105_0090
rows.name: Ah! It's that Blade again!

rows.label: qst201105_0100
rows.name:
No doubt about it. It's the other Blade from
the Core Crystal hunters.

rows.label: qst201105_0110
rows.name: Her name was Seori, right...?

rows.label: qst201105_0120
rows.name: So it WAS you...

rows.label: qst201105_0130
rows.name:
You were the one who kept messing with
us in the middle of battle, weren't you?

rows.label: qst201105_0140
rows.name: What do you want from us?

rows.label: qst201105_0150
rows.name: If you've got something to say, then say it.

rows.label: qst201105_0170
rows.name:
The message said the reward would be 'memories',
but I just can't figure out what's going on.

rows.label: qst201105_0180
rows.name:
We've been playing along with you for long
enough. It ends here!

rows.label: qst201105_0190
rows.name: So it didn't work...

rows.label: qst201105_0200
rows.name: What didn't work? Tell me!

rows.label: qst201105_0210
rows.name: *sigh*

rows.label: qst201105_0220
rows.name: Read the message. It's the last one.

rows.label: qst201105_0230
rows.name: Hey!
